- Bug Fixes
- Order with Skip the line! 

You don’t like waiting in lines? Than our new feature was designed for you! Log in to our application and choose Skip the line. Choose the restaurant where you would like to pick up your order, choose your favorite KFC meal and at the end pay through the application. If you finished just go to the choosen restaurant at the time you set to pick up your order. *Skip the line is only available at KFC West End, KFC Kiraly Street and KFC Deak Square. We are continuously working to expand the feature for all restaurants in Hungary.
